=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex9 ===

DESCRIPTION: A neutral gritty sound, with square_like oscillator character around 903 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally rich.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: neutral
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: gritty
  spectral_complexity_mean: rich
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 903.1866
  harmonic_decay_rate: -6.7261
  harmonic_regularity: 0.9653
  pitch_clarity: 18.5781
  inharmonicity: 0.2245
  type: square_like
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -25.4830
  resonance_freq: 947.4609

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Tour of UGens Example 9
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Guides/Tour_of_UGens.html
// Tags: Tour_of_UGens, Guides
